                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">偏向于讲述一战中英国军队的作战情况，东线非常简略。这书翻译的其实还算可以，但是存在大量的低级错误--错字、漏字、病句等等，明显没有上心。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="859124711">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-859124711" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-859124711" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="859124711">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1346689/">1997xhp</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-11-05</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">简要，文笔一般。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="839715621">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-839715621" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-839715621" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="839715621">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/paome/">岁月的泡沫</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">以战役介绍为主，挺好，就是错字太多，新华的这套都存在这个问题。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="814391247">
        <div class="comment">
