    <div class="main review-item" id="6695933">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6695933/" class="title-link">可以配合《一战秘史》一起看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6695933"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-06-08"
      class="main-meta">2014-06-08 18:22:08</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6695933_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  今年是一战爆发一百周年，满以为国内的出版商会趁此机会多出几本一战史的书，结果，半年过去了，就只有这么一本而已。 《一战秘史》、《一战倒计时》与《世界大战1914~1918》都是新华出版社在这几年推出的作品，这个选题还是蛮不错的（虽说翻译奇烂无比，这个待会儿再提）。《...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6695933/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
